NTFS 2.1.3a is now released for kernel 2.4.20.  This fixes all known
problems with the driver.  If you are still experiencing problems please
let us know.

Download the patch from:

	http://linux-ntfs.sf.net/downloads.html

Or get from our BK repository (which is at the current BK linux-2.4
version, i.e. 2.4.21-rc1-bk): 

	bk://linux-ntfs.bkbits.net/ntfs-2.4

